<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - 18 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO-14618 AND RTLO-16618
        SERIES - INSTALL - GEAR SHIFT LEVER HOUSING ASSEMBLY
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc id="hl1301905" svcproctype="install" graphiccount="2">
        <title>GEAR SHIFT LEVER HOUSING ASSEMBLY</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Check the shifter housing assembly to make sure shift block and yoke notches are aligned in
                the neutral position (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13019t3">Figure 293</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13019t3" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13019t3" filename="../figg13/G13019T3.webp" type="webp" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 293. Make Sure Shift Block and Yoke Notches Are Aligned in Neutral Position</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the shift lever housing on the shifter housing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13019t4">Figure 294</hotlnk>). Apply Loctite 242 or equivalent to the bolt threads and
                tighten the bolts to 35 to 45 ft-lbs. (47 to 61 N&#183;m).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13019t4" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13019t4" filename="../figg13/G13019T4.webp" type="webp" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 294. Install Shift Lever Housing on Shifter Housing</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
